----------------------------------------------------------------------
araa47 / wyoming_pocket_tts  —  https://github.com/araa47/wyoming_pocket_tts
----------------------------------------------------------------------
The original Wyoming-protocol wrapper around Kyutai Pocket TTS was
written by araa47, licensed under MIT. Polyglot TTS forks from this
work and adds:

  - Multi-language same-voice loading
  - Lingua-based automatic Language ID
  - Sentence-buffering for HA-aware streaming
  - num2words-driven text normalization (de/en/fr)
  - Mukser-Fix (fade-in + tail-padding to suppress chunk-boundary clicks)
  - CUDA support across amd64 + arm64 (Blackwell)
  - OpenAI-Speech-compatible HTTP endpoint
  - File-watcher voice-cloning workflow
  - REST API for voice management

